  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>City Zoomer</strong> is a fast-paced <strong>movement</strong> focused endless runner. Endless streets filled with unpredictable drivers are ahead. Zoom your way through the city at fast speeds to see how long you can last before making careless mistakes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Weekly leaderboards</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Co-op multiplayer</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Music</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Equipped with socks</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can You Last the Whole Night?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745790/extras/2d3817680d0f9d7c6c6ca55c18505108.avif?t=1751054788\" width=640 height=472 /></span></p>",
